Package org.dei.facts.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiagnosticParser
    The DiagnosticParser class is responsible for parsing diagnostic rules from a file and constructing a state graph based on the parsed rules.
    DiagnosticPath
    The DiagnosticPath class represents a diagnostic path with a diagnosis, a list of state names, and a list of applied rules.
    ImportFile  
    RuleInfo
    The RuleInfo class represents information about a diagnostic rule, including its name, current state, text conditions, and the root node of the "then" block.
    StateNode
    The StateNode class represents a state in the diagnostic state graph.
    ThenActionNode
    The ThenActionNode class represents an action node in the "then" block of a rule.
    ThenConditionNode
    The ThenConditionNode class represents a condition node in the "then" block of a rule.
    ThenElseNode
    The ThenElseNode class represents an "else" node in the "then" block of a rule.
    ThenSequenceNode
    The ThenSequenceNode class represents a sequence of ThenNode objects in the "then" block of a rule.
    Transition
    The Transition class represents a transition in a state machine.
